            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 pl-md-5 ftco-animate">
                <h2 class="mb-4">Welcome to WEEGCI Established Since 2022</h2>
                <p>Women Economic Empowerment and Girls Counseling Initiative (WEEGCI) is a nonprofit and non- governmental organization dedicated to improving women’s economic wellbeing through skills acquisition and training.</p>
                
